HEADWORD: Attempter
<hw>At*tempt"er</hw> <pr>(?; 215)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who attempts; one who essays anything.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An assailant; also, a temper.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Attemptive</ent>⟦br⟧
